Looking for a great little 'short smoke?' Say hello to our delicious Famous Stubbies Maduro. Handmade in the DR with a rich-tasting blend of Dominican Piloto Cubano, Criollo '98, and Nicaraguan longfillers, Olor binder, and a dark, savory Brazilian Arapiraca wrapper, these petites are sure to please.
